Analysis of the distribution of LTTRs across the P. aeruginosa pangenome


1. Perform CD Hit at 80%
biolinux@biolinux-VirtualBox[cd_hit_80]  cd-hit -i galaxy_no_duplicates.fa -o seqs -c 0.8 -n 5 -M 0 

2. Perform Muscle Alignment
biolinux@biolinux-VirtualBox[cd_hit_80] muscle -in seqs -phyiout reps_muscle 

3. Use Phyml online website.

4. RStudio to manipulate the data from the CD Hit results using the dplyr package v0.8.3 and to create visualisations using the
ggplot2 package v3.2.0 
